{"lastModified":1748603458142,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::c3f4b620-3a4e-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nYOUR FAMILY GETAWAY\nThe Lagoon 450F is renowned for its lovely features, spaciousness, and comfort. It is a popular alternative for individuals looking to enjoy yachting with their family or friends. The Lagoon 450F provides abundant indoor and outdoor space space for calmness, pleasure, and gathering.\n\nTHINK BIGGER\n\nReplacing a catamaran of reference is always a difficult exercise. The architects at VPLP, together with Lagoon and the famous design firm, Nauta, have nonetheless met the challenge with brio in creating the 450F. To think bigger on the interior, on the exterior, in features, and in performance…\n\nGO FURTHER\n\nWith additional options for comfort, equip your catamaran to sail far away on an extended cruise. The agility of the Lagoon 450F guarantees her maneuverability. Your stay on board will truly be a luxurious experience, with her contemporary style and comfortable living spaces.\n\nA BRIGHT INTERIOR\n\nWarm and spacious interior accommodations are bathed in natural light. The owner’s cabin is well ventilated by numerous hatches and windows in the hull. Take in the panoramic view from the saloon.","blueprint":{"name":"CELENA B","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::c3f4b620-3a4e-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::af2fcc80-3a52-11f0-a8b7-a9f841f6341d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c3f4b620-3a4e-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::af326490-3a52-11f0-a8b8-a9f841f6341d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c3f4b620-3a4e-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::af4d8db0-3a52-11f0-a8b9-a9f841f6341d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c3f4b620-3a4e-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::af308fd0-3a52-11f0-a8b7-a9f841f6341d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c3f4b620-3a4e-11f0-b715-e32b77698d18::assets::af326490-3a52-11f0-a8b9-a9f841f6341d/{im